    <description><![CDATA[Reason is the Rack and the devices. Reason is a plugin and a DAW. Reason is the wires and the workflow. Reason is your musical ideas and your final result.  

## Package Parameters
This package supports the following package parameters:
* `/NoVst` - Do not install the VST3 version
* `/NoAax` - Do not install the AAX version
* `/InstallationPath` - The path to install the standalone application to
* `/NoDesktopIcon` - Do not create a shortcut on the desktop
* `/WithoutSoundbanks` - Do not install/modify the soundbanks (you need ensure that the soundbanks exist at `%programdata%\Propellerhead Software\Soundbanks`)

For example, this is how you can use them: 
```
--package-parameters "'/NoAax /InstallationPath:${env:PROGRAMFILES}\AudioTools\Propellerhead\Reason 12 /NoDesktopIcon /WithoutSoundbanks '"
```
